\Delta ^{n}f(x)=\sum_{i=0}^{n}(-1)^{n-i}\binom{n}{i}f(x+i\Delta x)
\lim_{\Delta x\rightarrow 0} \frac{\Delta ^{n}f(x)}{\Delta x^{n}} = \lim_{\Delta x\rightarrow 0} \frac{\sum_{i=0}^{n}(-1)^{n-i}\binom{n}{i}f(x+i\Delta x)}{\Delta x^{n}} = f^{(n)}(x)
